    "notes": "Elixir allows dynamic typing; Scala requires explicit types.\n\n```elixir\n# Elixir - dynamic\ndef process(data) do\n  case data do\n    x when is_integer(x) -> x * 2\n    x when is_binary(x) -> String.length(x)\n    x when is_list(x) -> length(x)\n  end\nend\n```",
